column5: I'M GOING FISHING THE LAST WEEK IN MAY ON RAINY RIVER CAN ANYONE TELL ME WHAT THE FISHING IS LIKE?????

the fishing is always great on the river lake of the woods west is great and rainy lake is also a must fish lake all connected by the rainy river. stergeon fishing on the river is fantasticas well as walleye bass northern crapi even moon eyes can be caught. the world record moon eye was caught on the river
